    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_10_1673-1723",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1673-1723",
      "markText": "“不过股长，女人嘴馋，即便不饿，当同伴吃东西的时候，也会去陪着吃点喝点什么，比如布丁、咖啡什么的。”",
      "totalCount": 608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1723",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1673&rangeEnd=1723"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_14_1688-1722",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1688-1722",
      "markText": "“不关你的事。”鸟饲顶了她一句，他因刚才妻子未能陪自己喝茶而不能释怀",
      "totalCount": 391,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1688&rangeEnd=1722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1688&rangeEnd=1722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_52_3406-3437",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "3406-3437",
      "markText": "真是糊涂！名字不必是同一人的啊，用不同的名字去订票不就行了嘛。",
      "totalCount": 391,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=3406&rangeEnd=3437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=3406&rangeEnd=3437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_51_1105-1169",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "1105-1169",
      "markText": "他几乎惊叫起来。为何一直没有留意到这一点呢？他顿时耳鸣不已。他跑回房间，用哆嗦着的手指翻开时刻表的最后一页——日本航空的时刻表。",
      "totalCount": 286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=1105&rangeEnd=1169",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=1105&rangeEnd=1169"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_59_13076-13114",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "13076-13114",
      "markText": "反而认为是自知死期不远的亮子又施诡计，让丈夫与其同归于尽。亮子就是那种女人。",
      "totalCount": 276,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=13076&rangeEnd=13114",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=13076&rangeEnd=13114"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_59_10887-10971",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "10887-10971",
      "markText": "考虑到亮子身体病弱，被医生禁止与丈夫行房事，便不难想象阿时作为丈夫的情人是亮子承认和接受的。虽然关系扭曲得令人难以想象，但其实这种事社会上常有，在封建时代更是司空见惯。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=10887&rangeEnd=10971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=10887&rangeEnd=10971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_15_1286-1376",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1286-1376",
      "markText": "弟弟肯定不明白男女间所谓的逢场作戏，他被情场老手玩弄，还在人家死乞白赖之下与之殉情。那女的肯定是走投无路非死不可才把我弟弟拉去做伴的。对这个毁我弟弟大好前途的女人，我恨得咬牙切齿。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1286&rangeEnd=1376",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1286&rangeEnd=1376"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_59_11254-11278",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "11254-11278",
      "markText": "亮子是个可怕的女人，头脑冷静清晰，为人冷血无情。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=11254&rangeEnd=11278",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=11254&rangeEnd=11278"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_6_3231-3264",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3231-3264",
      "markText": "不过，那个阿时却被发现与同行的男子一起，死在了一个意想不到的地方。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3231&rangeEnd=3264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3231&rangeEnd=3264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_5_2057-2081",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2057-2081",
      "markText": "这时，他又看了一下手表。两人心想，他可真爱看表。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2081",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2081"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_29_2026-2048",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "2026-2048",
      "markText": "三原取出笔记本。只听一次，还是不能全弄明白。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2026&rangeEnd=2048",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=2026&rangeEnd=2048"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_51_1888-1944",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "1888-1944",
      "markText": "再看同一线路的下行列车。两点五十分离开函馆的快车球藻号，不正好在七点五十一分到达小樽吗？有一小时零七分的充裕时间",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=1888&rangeEnd=1944",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=1888&rangeEnd=1944"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_28_725-809",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "725-809",
      "markText": "三原一人忽然脱离了这一轨道五六天，然而没有一个人知晓他在这段空缺时间里干了什么，也没有人关心他看见了什么异常的事物，每个人的表情都很漠然。这虽然理所当然，他却怅然若失。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=725&rangeEnd=809",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=725&rangeEnd=809"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_23_469-479",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "469-479",
      "markText": "令人不由得联想到箱子",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=469&rangeEnd=479",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=469&rangeEnd=479"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_6_1590-1611",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1590-1611",
      "markText": "事后查对时，发现这趟车是六点零一分到站的。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1590&rangeEnd=1611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1590&rangeEnd=1611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_53_2577-2598",
      "chapterUid": 53,
      "range": "2577-2598",
      "markText": "没有一人使用化名。名单上的乘客都真实存在。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=53&rangeStart=2577&rangeEnd=2598",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=53&rangeStart=2577&rangeEnd=2598"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_9_1529-1567",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1529-1567",
      "markText": "因为很明显是殉情，刑警们神情轻松，有一种事不关己的味道——没有必要寻找罪犯。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1529&rangeEnd=1567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1529&rangeEnd=1567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_51_857-905",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "857-905",
      "markText": "三原无论如何也要让安田在二十号晚上十点至十一点之间出现在九州香椎的殉情现场，理由不妨以后再考虑。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=857&rangeEnd=905",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed632880813ab9043g019980?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=857&rangeEnd=905"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300106919_59_1101-1160",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "1101-1160",
      "markText": "下班回家泡在大水盆中，享用着井水冷却的啤酒，令我怀念起玄界滩的寒风，记得那一次您带我到香椎海边，我们曾任海风狂吹脸颊。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300106919&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=1101&rangeEnd=1160",
